thread.title: JADA U

author: JADA U
title: JADA U
text: The trees I ordered from Willis Orchards are top-notch. I bought a white oak that has a lovely thick trunk and two shagbark hickories. They gave me an extra hickory! Hickories have notoriously long taproots and are hard to transplant, so I guess they gave me another chance. Shipping was exactly on time zone-wise and delivered Fed-Ex to my door. These are two varieties that most nurseries don't carry.
